                                        <rs type="monuList" ref="https://www.slsgazetteer.org/1228">Sanctuary of Apollo</rs>, 'in the temple of Demeter' (see commentary).</p>
                                </provenance>
                                <provenance type="observed" when="1983" when-iso="2001" resp="cdl">
